snippet.title: [METALLIC CHILD] FIRST TRAILER
snippet.description:
Devloped by STUDIO HG
C.V : MyosongE (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClWTMxooQefOLUV0TRcJ1Eg/featured)

'Metallic Child' is a Roguelike action game.
It is currently under development and will be released in Summer 2019.
You can play on PC & Console.
